ttp://mitakusaner.blog.fc2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmitakusaner.blog.fc2.com%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HMmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=17d5d6ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mitakusaner.blog.fc2.com/</a></span></strong><br />\n</div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SKYRIM版本分別</strong></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">LE</span>版=The Elder Scrolls V:Skyrim Legendary Edition<br />\n&gt;本體+3DLC組合,<span style=\"color: red;\">2011年原版,Steam己下架停售</span>,需要另外上網買Key<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">SE</span>版=The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Special Edition<br />\n&gt;本體己包含3DLC,<span style=\"color: gold;\">2016年新版,Steam現售主流版本</span></strong>,包括Ps4,switch,VR平台全是SE版"},{"pid":"b95e11403018569f5edc52bf9dc4158f59632217","tid":1142868,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/images/1704/764085-1556505615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticdelivery.nexusmods.com%2Fimages%2F1704%2F764085-1556505615.png&h=2f9b4235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ:想入手Skyrim?<br />\nA:基本上新人想有最好既原遊戲體驗建議直接入手SE版本,SE版除MOD數量之外各方面都比LE優勝同穩定.就算之後想嘗試玩mod,SE亦有SE獨家同大部份LE既mod<br />\n<br />\nQ:有LE版想試下玩mod?<br />\nA:LE版-MOD新手教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cbdbrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cbdbrT</a><br />\nLE版人物美化推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cbdbsT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cbdbsT</a><br />\n<br />\nQ:我有SE版又想玩MOD<br />\nA:請參考上面新手教學,但SKSE需要SE版<br />\n<br />\nQ:LE成日彈game<br />\nA:<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=2526&amp;snA=32572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D2526%26snA%3D32572&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HMmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=84c078c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=2526&amp;snA=32572</a><br />\n跟著3樓教學<br />\n<br />\nQ:ENB係?<br />\nA:畫面材質美化,LE/SE皆有,請考慮自己硬件程度選擇<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以上只適用於PC版SKYRIM</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ:eso同skyrim係咪同一隻game既online版?<br />\nA:佢地係兩隻<span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔同</span>既game,只係時空背景ー樣<br />\n軟件,玩法上既野都完全唔會套用係對方<br />\n<br />\nQ:上古卷軸系列有咩game可以連機玩?<br />\nA:Elder Scrolls online(RPG online)/Elder Scrolls:League(卡牌game)/Elder Scrolls:Blade(手機新作)"},{"pid":"242b22e83be628d188f5a3d764c2a7f0b4c90b98","tid":1142868,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news-cdn.softpedia.com/images/news2/The-Elder-Scrolls-Online-May-Become-Free-to-Play-in-Less-Than-6-Months-Report-468693-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-cdn.softpedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnews2%2FThe-Elder-Scrolls-Online-May-Become-Free-to-Play-in-Less-Than-6-Months-Report-468693-2.jpg&h=d29cc356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ:eso其實係玩乜?<br />\nA:一般RPG做既野,農夫,劇情豐富既主線支任<br />\nPVP有聯盟國戰(根據天生種族選定,但可以課金解決)<br />\n<br />\nQ:我想入坑ESO?<br />\nA:<span style=\"color: gold;\">The Elder Scrolls Online Standard Edition</span>,全體一致推薦入坑包<br />\n我肯定自己可以長玩&gt;&gt;<span style=\"color: gold;\">The Elder Scrolls Online: Collection</span><br />\n想長玩又等最新大改版&gt;&gt;<span style=\"color: gold;\">The Elder Scrolls Online - Elsweyr</span><br />\n有錢人&gt;&gt;<span style=\"color: gold;\">The Elder Scrolls Online - Elsweyr Digital Collector's Edition</span><br />\n回坑&gt;&gt;直接買個最新DLC update或者上一個大改版DLC update,同樣有土豪版<br />\n<br />\nQ:eso有咩ser可以玩?可唔可以跨平台(pc,ps4,etc)?<br />\nA:NA北美/EU西歐,唔可以跨平台<br />\n<br />\nQ:eso呢度有冇公會<br />\nA:有,但大部份人都半afk狀態<br />\n<br />\nQ:tg?<br />\nA:我地得discord,一樣eso/skyrim為主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有其他問題係下面問<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>歡迎各位巴絲入黎討論上古卷軸嘅任何野,不論任何平台<br />\n因為會有講故佬解答</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">是樓主我</span></span>